                  {
                    "value": "The finding. ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "12pt",
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#3987e5",
                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Acting on the churn model alone \u2014 contacting every customer it flags \u2014 loses ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "12pt",
                      "color": "#ffffff",
                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "R144,018",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "12pt",
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#e66767",
                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": ". Contacting only the 2,218 customers whose expected recovery exceeds the R60 cost returns ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "12pt",
                      "color": "#ffffff",
                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "R39,662",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "12pt",
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "color": "#3987e5",
                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": ", a 30% return on spend. The gap is roughly R184,000 and none of it comes from a better model \u2014 the probabilities are identical in both cases. The value was in deciding who to leave out.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "12pt",
                      "color": "#ffffff",
                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
