              },
              {
                "horizontalTextAlignment": "left",
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Assumptions: R60 cost per contact (R20 admin + R40 offer) and a 30% retention success rate, both stated in sql/05_economics.sql. The success rate is the least certain input; below about 25% the programme stops being worth running.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "10pt",
